instruction: Construct a list of skills to put on a resume for a machine learning position.
output:
- Programming Skills: Python, C/C++, Java
- Machine Learning Algorithms: Neural Networks, Decision Trees, SVM, K-Means Clustering
- Machine Learning Libraries: TensorFlow, Scikit-Learn, Keras
- Data Analysis Tools: Pandas, Numpy, Matplotlib
- Data Manipulation & Visualization: SQL, Tableau
- Model Evaluation: Cross-Validation, K-Fold
- Project Management: Agile, Scrum
- Communication & Collaboration: Documentation, Presentations, Team Communication
